Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:43.35,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Environmental concerns and the \Nincreasing scarcity of fossil fuels
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:47.45,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,have led to the cessation in the manufacture \Nof cars with internal combustion engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:51.77,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, high-powered sports cars \Nhave become an endangered species.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:57.52,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Almost as a requiem to mourn their \Nimminent passing, a new motorsport series
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:59.66,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,has arisen here in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:04.66,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,With a global audience \Nof 30 million subscribers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.81,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,it has achieved explosive popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:14.64,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The only regulation is \Nuniform grip-to-weight ratio,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:18.76,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,resulting in some no-holds-barred,\Nwhite-knuckle racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:22.97,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Its name: MFG.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:27.98,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.2\bord0\fnImpact\shad0\fs90\b1\c&H0100D1&\pos(330,110)}MF Ghost
