Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.46,0:01:33.09,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(330,580)\bord0.5\shad1.5\b1\fnArial\blur0.3\fax-0.15\pos(504,298)\3c&H5B5B5B&\t(4050,4620,\blur5)}The Challenger \Nfrom England
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:33.82,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,It's the MFG season opener, \Nand we're here at Odawara Pikes Peak
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.82,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,for the start of the \Nsecond day of qualifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:40.29,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Ten seconds to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.74,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Nine. Eight. Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:46.16,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Six. Five. Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.92,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Three. Two. One.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:01.46,Default,Passenger A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Aiba. You've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:03.33,Default,Passenger B,0000,0000,0000,,He's really going for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:06.06,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,MFG, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:10.17,Default,Passenger C,0000,0000,0000,,Just once, I wish I could go\N see them race in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:13.77,Default,Passenger D,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening. They don't let\Nspectators line the route,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:18.65,Default,Passenger D,0000,0000,0000,,and there's still volcanic gas \Nin the air from that eruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:21.91,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,My friends in England \Nwere all obsessed with it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.44,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense it's popular here,\N as it started in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:30.40,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly can't make head or tail of \Nthese addresses. Talk about a bad start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.92,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.71,Italics,Wakana,0000,0000,0000,,The English guy is showing up today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:40.42,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Technically, he's half-English, half-Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.18,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get your hopes up, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.29,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get cool vibes from England.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:48.33,Italics,Wakana,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you're no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.57,Italics,Wakana,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better introduce me if he's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.98,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Get real, Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.19,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you go after anyone hot \Nthat you always end up with lame guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.67,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even imagine love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:04.66,Flashback,Shun,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. I'm Aiba Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:10.29,Flashback,Shun,0000,0000,0000,,I came in ninth last year, and, um,\N from the moment I first saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.50,Flashback,Shun,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:14.69,Flashback,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:15.38,Flashback,Shun,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:20.22,Flashback,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you expect me to react \Nwhen you don't know anything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.33,Flashback,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, just one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.30,Flashback,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,On the MFG Angels' profile page,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:28.02,Flashback,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,you're the only one listed \Nwithout any info, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:31.35,Flashback,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Could you at least tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:36.55,Flashback,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,MFGA Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:40.11,Flashback,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(2050,3550,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}You can call me Number Seven, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:45.70,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Looks are basically the same as clothes. \NThey don't reflect who you {\i0}really{\i1} are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:50.54,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna fall in love with \Na guy who {\i0}I{\i1} think is super hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:55.27,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,even if 99% of girls don't \Nagree with me that he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:58.92,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.05,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.17,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come in here and let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:08.09,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure I said I was gonna be late today \Nbecause of work. I told Mom, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.75,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H60&}This is Kanata-kun. Mr. Kanata Rivington.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.01,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H60&}He just got in this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:24.04,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H60&}This will be his first time living overseas,\N so I'm sure he'll have questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.62,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H60&}and I'd appreciate you helping \Nhim as much as you can, Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.52,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H60&}It's a pleasure to meet you, Ren-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.06,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H60&\t(700,900,\alpha&H00&)}You can call me Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.53,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:41.52,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I have math homework, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.80,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's at an awkward age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:52.43,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, I'm impressed by\Nhow fluent your Japanese is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.23,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,My mum taught me when I was still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.21,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:00.69,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real shame what \Nhappened to Katherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:05.49,Default,Ren Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You remind me a lot of her\N when she was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.99,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.25,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I just got shocked \Nwith a million volts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.04,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why's my heart still pounding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.71,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not supposed to judge \Npeople by appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.82,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,So... what is this feeling?
