Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.73,Top,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,MF Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.57,Default,Wakana,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.29,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.98,Default,Wakana,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the thing! C'mon, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.98,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:03.88,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.80,Default,Wakana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god! Can you believe it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:14.13,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Kanata really is hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.38,Flashback,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:19.38,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,A picture from 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.35,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And the only one I have of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:27.99,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I love that photo because of how \Nhappy my mother looks in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:30.56,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It was taken in a town called Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:37.00,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that, if I ever made it to Japan, \NI'd find the location in that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.86,Flashback,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Kamakura's pretty close by. I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.62,Flashback,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I help you find it, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.31,Flashback,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a really romantic idea, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.10,Flashback,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you find this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.59,Flashback,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:59.05,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so kind to me, Ren?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:04.01,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know how \Nto express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:08.39,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,You and your father have \Njust been so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.81,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.55,Flashback,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese people are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.99,Default,Yamashita,0000,0000,0000,,It's not happening, Aiba-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.37,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on. Don't be such a stickler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.85,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,All I'm asking for is\NNumber Seven's name and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.00,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HAF6CBA&\bord0\shad0\fs12\blur0.3\frz3.071\pos(202.667,258)}Profile\N{\fs9}Name: ? Birthday: ? Birthplace: ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:31.00,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,You've posted all kinds of stuff \Nabout the other Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:34.89,Default,Yamashita,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of personal information \Nis confidential. No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:38.39,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Then, could you at least tell me \Nwhich race she's working next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.97,Default,Yamashita,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:44.11,Default,Lady Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Kanata-san.\N If you'll just sign here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:44.89,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.85,Italics,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Never seen him before. Is he a rookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:53.18,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.15,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,You entering MFG?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.94,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:01.90,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aiba Shun. I'm ranked\N a dizzyingly high ninth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:05.62,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know you! Aiba in the Nissan GT-R!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.47,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! It's truly an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:11.63,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,People love your GT-R back in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.50,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,England?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.35,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I arrived from there two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.64,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kanata Rivi—Wait, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:21.59,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Katagiri Kanata. \NI'm running on the last day of qualifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:25.30,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you're gonna be okay?\N This is MFG we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.18,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's fine. \NI bet we met for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.64,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind taking you \Nunder my wing for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:35.73,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Kanata.\NFrom now on, you call me "Senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.86,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,We're big sticklers for the beauty of\N tradition around here. You follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.57,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Aiba-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:45.16,Italics,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man. I love how earnest this dude is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:50.87,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArial\fs18\fax0.13\fscx72\fay0.21\bord0\shad0\c&HAAAE88&\pos(459.334,115.334)\frx0\fry10}Odawara\N\h{\fay0.19}Office
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:49.59,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat yet? I'll treat you to a \Ngreat Japanese lunch. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.49,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:54.41,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,He's steadily moving up the times\Nthrough Sector 3 of the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.54,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one car \Nbetween him and top spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:59.78,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Michael Beckenbauer's \Nshowing no sign of weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:04.09,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Am I imagining it or is that \NPorsche smaller than a regular one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.09,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad0\blur0.3\fs10\pos(96,201.334)\frz358.6\3c&H535CAF&\c&H65E4E9&}Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.09,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad0\blur0.3\fs8\3c&H535CAF&\c&H65E4E9&\pos(413.333,202)\frz356.7}Beef\h\hBowl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.09,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad0\blur0.3\fs7\3c&H7D84CC&\c&H65E4E9&\pos(472,102.667)\frz355.3}Beef Bowl + Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.09,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad0\blur0.3\fs7\3c&H9294AD&\c&HE9E3F6&\frz355.3\pos(448.667,128.667)}Open
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:09.26,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Cayman. They're about \Na size smaller than the 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.11,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously didn't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:15.37,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Beckenbauer's straight out of \NPorsche's motorsports program.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.48,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,He's some kinda super-elite racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.69,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,He would probably have been a \NLe Mans driver in the good old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:25.45,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs14\bord1.5\shad0\blur0.3\fax-0.1\3c&H154B41&\c&H27E8D7&\frz340\pos(339.333,24.001)}Qualifying Run {\alpha&HFF&\t(980,981,\alpha&H00&)}/ 1st Position
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.45,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great. He's made it to \Nthe top of the leaderboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:30.91,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell is he managing these times \Nwith the kind of power a Cayman has?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.91,Default,Server,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.29,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.73,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Beef bowls are a delicacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.29,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.88,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you anyway, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.13,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.94,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that's young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.22,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Five years younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.18,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you don't know how to use chopsticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:55.44,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, miss. Could you bring this guy a spoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.48,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fsp5\fnVerdana\fs22\c&H4A443A&\pos(324.667,208)\frz1.471}Ogata Automotive Lt{\fsp1}d.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.85,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Are you around, Ogata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.80,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.07,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.46,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see if there was \Nanything I could help you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:15.25,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure. I was looking \Nto take a break, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.71,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnComic Sans MS\fs19\frz358\c&H12FAF7&\3c&H042C2B&\pos(439,210)}Koala's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.71,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnComic Sans MS\fs14\fax-0.7\c&H12FAF7&\3c&H042C2B&\frz48.21\frx346\fry34\pos(487.333,188.666)}March
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.08,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:24.16,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have snacks anywhere \Nnear as good as this in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.25,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Japan is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.72,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Between this and beef bowls, \Nit's like everything you guys eat is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.54,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.56,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit the snacks here are good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:41.90,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, Kanata, \None of my cars has raced in MFG before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:46.76,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been refitted since, \Nso it should easily pass the inspection,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.70,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no real need\N to make big changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.61,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.24,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,You, Ogata-san? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.24,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. Call it a youthful misadventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.72,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,I used to race back then, and was \Npretty confident about my skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.68,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't amount to much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.87,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,The downhill stretch in \NSector 3 scared me so bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.30,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,by the time I crossed the finish line, \NI was heartbroken and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:17.27,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,What it boils down to is I'm better suited \Nto tinkering with cars than driving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:22.23,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArial\fscx60\fax-0.7\fs20\bord0.2\shad1.5\pos(148.667,120.667)\c&H7E7776&\3c&H7F736E&\4c&H6E6E70&\frz21.18\frx346\fry346}Ogata Automotive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:21.79,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Can't deny how much I love these \Nold gasoline models, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.65,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.83,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,The buildings in the background \Nseem totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:36.00,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it was taken on the \Ngrounds of a shrine or a temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:41.14,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,And wouldn't you know it? Kamakura's \Nabsolutely crawling with spots like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:45.27,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to use process of \Nelimination to work through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:46.77,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.81,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It really does feel strange, being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:57.18,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,So much so, it's hard for me\N to put it into Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.94,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:03.85,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,My mother met my father here \Nwhen she was still just a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:09.16,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,They fell in love, \Nlived together, then I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:15.24,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Being here in Kamakura is unbelievable. \NLike something out of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:19.33,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I've come to \Nthe hometown of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:22.83,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to visit\N ever since I was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.86,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.13,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata, let's make an offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.84,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,He's so earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:41.48,Italics,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.39,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fscx80\bord0.1\blur0.3\xshad-3\fay0.16\fs36\pos(271.333,143.333)\3c&HC6C6C6&\c&HF7F7F7&}Asakura Komachi Road
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:46.65,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,What did you wish for, Ren?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.53,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:53.72,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell someone else,\Nthe gods might not hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.40,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, it's already late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.79,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, Mom, I've got work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.49,Default,Mayuko,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:07.44,Default,Mayuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trip in your rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.70,Default,Mayuko,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.88,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.24,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Ren's got work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.85,Italics,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And I have an event of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:21.85,Default,Joyu,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. This is Joyu \Nwith the Tokyo Main Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:25.25,Default,Joyu,0000,0000,0000,,The Executive Organizer \Nmade a direct request.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:28.44,Default,Joyu,0000,0000,0000,,There's a name on the entry list\N he was hoping to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.40,Default,Joyu,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata Rivington, 19 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.85,Default,Joyu,0000,0000,0000,,He's a British citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.44,Default,Joyu,0000,0000,0000,,Not there? That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:42.41,Default,Joyu,0000,0000,0000,,Did the kid Ryosuke mentioned not show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:47.29,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there to the 30 million \NMFG fans across the globe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:52.55,Default,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,I'm MFG's walking encyclopedia, Tanaka Yoji, \Nand I'll be providing live commentary today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.76,Default,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally the seventh \Nand last day of qualifying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:18:00.04,Default,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,and this round has been typified by a lot \Nof shakeups at the top of the timesheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.08,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to aggressive moves \Nby the Porsche camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:07.26,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,the Italian big hitters, Ferrari \Nand Lamborghini, have struggled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:13.07,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The hope of home nation manufacturers, \NAiba Shun and his GT-R, is currently in fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:17.43,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Odawara's own "Kamikaze \NOutlaw" is making waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:23.42,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Only 15 of the 302 entrants \Nwill make it into the race proper,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.75,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,earning them the title\N of the "Godly Fifteen."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.71,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The "Godly Fifteen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:31.04,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we gotta worry about \Nqualifying before anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:35.38,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,The new set of tires I put on\N should last for three races.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:40.32,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Ogata-san, I apologize if the tires\N are worn out after this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.35,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if I warn you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:48.27,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And there's the board. We have 10 seconds \Nleft before the first racer takes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:51.96,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,It's being held up by Number Seven, \Na new addition to the Angels this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:54.86,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,I'm personally a big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:59.61,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those curves! \NIt's enough to take your breath away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.55,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up, Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.95,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you get off, \Ncreeping on my Number Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.99,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And there's the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:11.33,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Just the sight of her makes my heart hurt.\N Number Seven, my darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.88,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Aiba-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:17.11,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, if it isn't Shun! It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.85,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Ogata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:22.83,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here? \NDidn't you already set a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:24.43,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:28.89,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to root for Kanata, \Nof course. I'm kinda worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.89,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,How do you even know Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:34.86,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Aiba-senpai bought me a beef bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.37,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into him at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.67,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's a hell of a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:41.37,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a small world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:45.58,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the chitchat will have to wait. \NWe've only got 10 minutes until the off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.99,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.33,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,You need any help? Which car is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.77,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,The one I used to race in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.81,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.41,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Number 86.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.21,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:13.53,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Got a few crucial pieces of info \Nfor you to remember, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:18.16,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing about\N qualifying is to finish the lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:19.98,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go damaging the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:23.53,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,A lap around Odawara Pikes Peak is 40 km.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.00,Top,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it the longest MFG course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:30.38,Top,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing this for a while, and even \NI don't have the whole thing memorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.41,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,You scope it out at all \Non the official website?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.30,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the course \Nlayout memorized, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.65,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,No way. How many hundreds\N of times did that take?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.92,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I think... only three?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.80,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for jokes, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.42,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. This thing \Ndoesn't have a ton of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:51.18,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll wanna go uphill at around 70%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.02,Top,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,It's hell going downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:57.98,Top,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,For Sector 3 in particular, you'll wanna \Npull back to around 50-60% there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:01.96,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll understand what \NI'm saying once you've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.26,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:08.37,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Car 86, please proceed \Nto the inspection table.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.33,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is a rookie \Nmaking his first appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:15.42,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Car 86, driven by a \Nchallenger from England.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.96,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Kanata, 19 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:19.96,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.97,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me? Is that really him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:33.98,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:39.05,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Six. Five. Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:39.31,Italics,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Is it me or did she just look\Nreally surprised for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:41.74,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Three. Two. One.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:47.54,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:36.16,Italics,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Turn 02: \NThe Shocking New MFG Generation.